---
// Hero section with animated background and CTA
---

<section
    class="relative min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center gradient-bg overflow-hidden"
>
    <!-- Decorative elements -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 overflow-hidden">
        <div
            class="absolute -top-40 -right-40 w-96 h-96 bg-tropical-400/10 rounded-full blur-3xl floating"
        >
        </div>
        <div
            class="absolute -bottom-40 -left-40 w-96 h-96 bg-ocean-400/10 rounded-full blur-3xl floating"
            style="animation-delay: -3s;"
        >
        </div>
        <div
            class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-[600px] h-[600px] bg-sand-400/5 rounded-full blur-3xl"
        >
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="relative z-10 text-center px-4 max-w-4xl mx-auto pt-20">
        <div
            class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/10 text-sm text-ocean-100 mb-8"
        >
            <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-tropical-400 animate-pulse"
            ></span>
            🌴 Tu próxima aventura comienza aquí
        </div>
        <h2
            class="font-heading font-extrabold text-5xl sm:text-6xl lg:text-7xl leading-tight mb-6"
        >
            <span class="block">Explora cada rincón de</span>
            <span
                class="bg-gradient-to-r from-sand-400 via-sunset-400 to-tropical-400 bg-clip-text text-transparent"
                >República Dominicana</span
            >
        </h2>
        <p
            class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-ocean-200 max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-10 leading-relaxed"
        >
            Descubre playas paradisíacas, montañas majestuosas y una cultura
            vibrante. Haz clic en cualquier provincia del mapa para explorar sus
            tesoros escondidos.
        </p>
        <a
            href="#mapa"
            class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 bg-gradient-to-r from-tropical-500 to-ocean-500 hover:from-tropical-400 hover:to-ocean-400 text-white font-heading font-semibold px-8 py-4 rounded-2xl text-lg shadow-lg shadow-tropical-500/30 hover:shadow-tropical-400/40 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-0.5"
        >
            <svg
                class="w-5 h-5"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            >
                <path
                    stroke-linecap="round"
                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                    stroke-width="2"
                    d="M9 20l-5.447-2.724A1 1 0 013 16.382V5.618a1 1 0 011.447-.894L9 7m0 13l6-3m-6 3V7m6 10l4.553 2.276A1 1 0 0021 18.382V7.618a1 1 0 00-.553-.894L15 4m0 13V4m0 0L9 7"
                ></path>
            </svg>
            Explorar el Mapa
        </a>

        <!-- Scroll indicator -->
        <div
            class="absolute bottom-8 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 flex flex-col items-center gap-2 text-ocean-300 text-xs"
        >
            <span>Desliza hacia abajo</span>
            <svg
                class="w-5 h-5 animate-bounce"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            >
                <path
                    stroke-linecap="round"
                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                    stroke-width="2"
                    d="M19 14l-7 7m0 0l-7-7m7 7V3"></path>
            </svg>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
